{"h600eedfeg9b1ag49bfg9a2bg0dbc6f7d04e8": ["*As you approach, a guttural scream and a succession of quick bangs rattle the door.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "4e8f5da9-1e2e-ea8d-17a5-d38043f0f062"], "hac86c845g1991g4e23g87c2g9e8992b61d26": ["*Then a low moan. Someone - or <i>something </i>- is having a bit of fun.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "1fac0de2-625e-9302-c091-f9e8dd9f1fae"], "h6aea3f99ga1e9g4621gaf2dge2ba7c195a31": ["<i>Open the door.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "fbc20e44-7df9-0951-7cd0-d7ad5adf57ee"], "hd7410105gfbf8g4f1egb99dg8262a947647e": ["Leave it. Whoever's inside doesn't want an audience, and I don't want a fight.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "94866875-2979-ce5c-8ec8-cb77161ed79b"], "hb6407c05gfff7g4eedg9304ga31b5087b57a": ["<i>Open the door anyway.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "13b5d507-a37f-d63c-f9f3-2b4f02b3daa0"], "h76a001fag63e7g4372g9b50g08f95cadb08c": ["Ngh. W-what the hells are you doin'?", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "c912d374-947e-f6af-2b7e-56c465aac732"], "hc0ec603ega8d6g4a17g968aga584ae6e4c42": ["Apologies. I didn't mean to interrupt.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "ad595a4b-d6ca-61e0-aa96-d4d471aa8b27"], "h0eebb9dcga90fg4d5bg9176g912bf82cc921": ["Ruined! Smash - I'll SMASH YOU!", "489c7f56-b461-41a6-b519-7ef5f1a1bbdc", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "e38cafc6-f255-04b8-fa45-dd951abc95ff"], "h704c8b69g44f7g4563ga176g0bd660c2da3e": ["You were making a lot of noise - I wanted to join the fun.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "be75c293-fc25-5c95-a347-2ed7828a4b1a"], "h5e098361gb05bg401ag96c1g9dcce8976424": ["<i>Back away slowly.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "93228ca7-baf2-f8d0-a777-81bd3077dcc4"], "h314dc14bg0ffbg41caga19fg849a78191145": ["<i>Attack the couple.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "8d953238-96dd-cee8-3adb-702a9c7eccfa"], "hd0d55244g67e5g45f1g9e15g197801e3a469": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "599f0a01-8174-583e-e9e3-a72ffe0f695d"], "h07525c21gcd46g4b55gbfafg12f8ae8e2071": ["In matters of the birds and the bees, best let nature take its sticky course.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "b3b6ec26-00b8-426c-79ba-b479be9ce762"], "h61ab873dg9a37g4466g9fc2gdc0c80dabdc1": ["Wait! Don't interrupt them.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "27ade790-8de8-f606-7826-4e68acab3020"], "hd3823a10g6d02g4c37ga8ecg36ba4f9fc07a": ["Let me do it. They sound <i>disgusting</i>.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "ad6161bf-1eb6-d469-313d-8090ad7ca881"], "h53fa2742g9c39g48a3g9725g2c8d91f3aa09": ["Please do the honours.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "78172827-827b-cb24-e34a-0f0bc6fbe235"], "h029e9dcag7503g461cga1aegd66a0fc7a281": ["Hello? Anybody in there? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "39e82735-0b5a-f5c9-d59a-8bf0cb7dea64"], "hff41ba63g745ag4a13g8e28g55ba1ed3bcf1": ["Go away.", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "e0c238c2-2a5f-0dc5-760e-301046e4063f"], "hca6a8cb0g7147g43bag9bfbg20e2a8ac7baf": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "0b5e1ad7-7ce9-2a0a-0c9b-7fbcb4bb7cfc"], "hf4ee329dg808fg4236gb810g604b4eb7b1ad": ["*You hear another muffled cry. The two inside are still in the throes of... passion.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "89a17e39-46b2-23c9-d3b8-2559bd7c9f4d"], "hca1fc9e8g361bg4d37g832eg43403cd26b86": ["Ngh. W-what the hells are you doin'?", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "26227233-0451-d4ff-2791-bd93d2c94da9"], "h542dc190g589eg46fega5cbg614b03ea5900": ["Ngh. W-what the hells are you doin'?", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "e1b3dfd8-68f0-df85-9c3e-8aa30155a60e"], "h181f163fg22feg4005g8b95gb396a23069db": ["What - what the hells are you doin?!", "b6c6764f-ba9d-4109-8b4e-c0d1da72be7d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BugBear.html", "ec5e8b61-f83f-4e90-10e0-21a9ae1d9349"]}